query:
SELECT 
                    "order".id as "id!",
                    market_id,
                    owner_id,
                    transaction_id,
                    "transaction".timestamp as transaction_timestamp,
                    size as "size: _",
                    price as "price: _",
                    side as "side: _"
                FROM "order"
                JOIN "transaction" on ("order".transaction_id = "transaction".id)
                WHERE market_id = ?
                ORDER BY "order".id
